{"word":"G4141 - πλήσσω - plḗssō - place'-so - Smite","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πλήσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">plḗssō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">place'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Smite</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சேதப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to strike, to smite"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Apparently another form of <a href=\"#/G4111 - πλάσσω - plássō - plas'-so/4111\">G4111</a> (through the idea of <i>flattening</i> out); to <i>pound</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>inflict</i> with (calamity): - smite. Compare <a href=\"#/G5180 - τύπτω - týptō - toop'-to/5180\">G5180</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}